&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for a &lt;strong&gt;Station Domestic/Cleaner&lt;/strong&gt; at &lt;strong&gt;Northampton North Ambulance Station, Northamptonshire.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant / applicants will be responsible for cleaning the stations to set Infection Prevention Control Guidelines. They must hold a full clean UK driving licence and may be required to travel on occasion to other stations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With a flexible approach to both hours and duties you must be reliable and have the ability to work without supervision. Relevant previous work experience would be an advantage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The working hours for these roles are as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Northampton North &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monday – 3 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Tuesday – 3 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wednesday – 3 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thursday – 3 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Friday – 3 hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Total 15 hours &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
